---
---

<section class="py-32 bg-surface-container-lowest" id="soluciones">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16 gap-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-4">
          Soluciones de Ingeniería
        </h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body">
          Infraestructura digital diseñada para la eficiencia absoluta.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="h-px bg-outline-variant flex-grow mx-8 hidden md:block"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      <!-- AI Automations - Large Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 group cursor-pointer card relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary">psychology</span>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-4">
          Automatizaciones con IA
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-md mb-8">
          Integramos agentes inteligentes que procesan datos, atienden clientes y optimizan decisiones en tiempo real. No solo IA generativa, sino lógica autónoma.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-sm text-[10px] font-mono text-secondary border border-secondary/10">
            LLM OPS
          </span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-sm text-[10px] font-mono text-secondary border border-secondary/10">
            NATURAL LANGUAGE
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Fullstack Development -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 card group">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-6">layers</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">
          Desarrollo Fullstack
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Arquitecturas escalables de punta a punta. Desde interfaces ultra-rápidas hasta backends resilientes.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Workflows -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 card group">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">account_tree</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">
          Flujos de Trabajo
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Conectamos tus herramientas favoritas para eliminar tareas manuales repetitivas y cuellos de botella.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Connected Ecosystems -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 card flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">
            Ecosistemas Conectados
          </h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Creamos puentes digitales entre tu inventario, CRM y canales de venta usando APIs personalizadas de alto rendimiento.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-high rounded-sm border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40">api</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-high rounded-sm border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40">database</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-high rounded-sm border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary/40">cloud_done</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
